### Relevant Package

This feature request is for @angular/core


### Description

I couldn't find the [docs on tree-shakable injectiontokens on the angular.io page](https://angular.io/api/core/InjectionToken#tree-shakable-injectiontoken)

Feature is already implemented.



### Describe the solution you'd like

```ts
export interface ButtonOptions {
  /* ... */
}

export const BUTTON_DEFAULTS: ButtonOptions = {
  /* ... */
};

@Injectable({
  providedIn: 'root',
  useValue: BUTTON_DEFAULTS
})
export const BUTTON_TOKEN = new InjectionToken<ButtonOptions>('ButtonOptions');
```


### Describe alternatives you've considered

Current workaround:

```ts
export interface ButtonOptions {
   defaultVariant: string;
}

export const BUTTON_DEFAULTS: ButtonOptions = {
  defaultVariant: 'foo'
};

/** @internal */
export function buttonOptionsFactory() {
  const o = new ButtonOptionsToken();
  Object.assign(o, BUTTON_DEFAULTS);

  return o;
}

/** @internal DI token for ButtonOptions interface */
@Injectable({
  providedIn: 'root',
  useFactory: buttonOptionsFactory
})
export class ButtonOptionsToken implements ButtonOptions {
  defaultVariant;
}
